  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191400/extras/65bf90cfc24b0c6be097359369aede0b.poster.avif?t=1759177522\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191400/extras/65bf90cfc24b0c6be097359369aede0b.webm?t=1759177522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191400/extras/65bf90cfc24b0c6be097359369aede0b.mp4?t=1759177522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're about to lose your mind. After school forced to move to a new city without friends and your beloved boyfriend. After one year all previous connections seem to be lost.. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be ready - it will get worse! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every day there are more and more lost people related to your university, A tendency that started after the previous Halloween and that grows even bigger to the next one </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have 31 days to face yourself and deep-deep evil from another world! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience day-to-day student life at Uni by attending lectures and practicing. And slash through enemies with witches' rituals to ascend to DreamWorld </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreamWorld consists of DevilGuardians that will hunt you down, Memory Rails for fast movement, and KillingThoughts as regular enemies </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hack and slash-throw enemies! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose why you are better than them with stats and characteristics to make you stronger! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your abilities and make every attempt a unique experience! </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191400/extras/65bf90cfc24b0c6be097359369aede0b.poster.avif?t=1759177522\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191400/extras/65bf90cfc24b0c6be097359369aede0b.webm?t=1759177522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191400/extras/65bf90cfc24b0c6be097359369aede0b.mp4?t=1759177522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're about to lose your mind. After school forced to move to a new city without friends and your beloved boyfriend. After one year all previous connections seem to be lost.. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be ready - it will get worse! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every day there are more and more lost people related to your university, A tendency that started after the previous Halloween and that grows even bigger to the next one </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have 31 days to face yourself and deep-deep evil from another world! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience day-to-day student life at Uni by attending lectures and practicing. And slash through enemies with witches' rituals to ascend to DreamWorld </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DreamWorld consists of DevilGuardians that will hunt you down, Memory Rails for fast movement, and KillingThoughts as regular enemies </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hack and slash-throw enemies! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose why you are better than them with stats and characteristics to make you stronger! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your abilities and make every attempt a unique experience! </p></li></ul>",
